1.1.name: wordpress/simon-wp-framework
1.1.description: A blank framework licensed under the GPL. It's a blank theme that provides the most flexibility for creating child themes from Simon WP Framework. Theme comes with custom icons. This Framework is widget ready in the sidebar and in the footer.
